      "questionNumber": 2,
      "questionText": "A mixture containing the following four compounds is extracted with $$1M$$ $$HCl.$$ The compound that goes to aqueous layer is :\n<br><br><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l83mrti0/1d8a9229-2bdf-461f-96c0-72d58c66c0f6/c169c270-3546-11ed-8c5c-f3f0850e6b94/file-1l83mrti1.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l83mrti0/1d8a9229-2bdf-461f-96c0-72d58c66c0f6/c169c270-3546-11ed-8c5c-f3f0850e6b94/file-1l83mrti1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2017 (Online) 8th April Morning Slot Chemistry - Basics of Organic Chemistry Question 246 English\">",
      "options": [
        "(I) ",
        "(II)",
        "(III)",
        "(IV)"
      ],
      "correctOption": 1,
      "correctAnswer": null,
      "questionType": "MCQ",
